						               													<description>Champions of Legarren is a fun, competitive fitness-based card game for 1-5 players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the game, you take on the role of one of five Champions to battle in an epic tournament for the glory of being crowned the Knight of Legarren.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each character has a deck of ability cards at their disposal.  To use those abilities, you must pass an exercise challenge.  The better you perform at that exercise challenge, the more powerful that ability becomes!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game has three modes: Training, Versus, and Tournament.  In Training mode, you work your way through your character's deck, practicing the movements and getting a great at-home workout.  In Versus mode, you challenge one other player to a duel, battling until one of you is victorious.  Finally, in Tournament mode, up to 5 players compete in an all-out battle royale to determine the Knight of Legarren.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
